  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparator<Object>, I_C_Invoice, IDocLine, IPODoc, Evaluatee, IBasePO, IPO, I_Persistent

    public class MInvoice
extends X_C_Invoice
implements I_C_Invoice, IPODoc
    Invoice Model. Please do not set DocStatus and C_DocType_ID directly. They are set in the process() method. Use DocAction and C_DocTypeTarget_ID instead.
    Version:

    Jorg Janke, victor.perez@e-evolution.com, e-Evolution http://www.e-evolution.com
    See Also:
